headline: Hain Celestial appoints Alison Lewis as president, CEO on permanent basis
summary: Lewis took on the roles in an interim capacity in May following the departure of Wendy Davidson.

headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks to Consider Right Now and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: While strong cash flow is a key indicator of stability, it doesn’t always translate to superior returns. Some cash-heavy businesses struggle with inefficient spending, slowing demand, or weak competitive positioning.
